          <h2>Our Affiliate Relationships</h2>
          <p>iRecommendU participates in affiliate marketing programs. This means we may earn a commission when you click on links to products or services and make a purchase. This comes at no additional cost to you.</p>
          <h2>Which Products We Link To</h2>
          <p>We have affiliate relationships with companies including but not limited to: Hostinger, Bluehost, Shopify, HubSpot, and others. When you see a "Get Deal" or "Visit" button on our site, it may be an affiliate link.</p>
          <h2>Our Editorial Independence</h2>
          <p>Affiliate commissions do not influence our reviews or recommendations. We only recommend products we genuinely believe are useful. If a product has major flaws, we will say so regardless of whether we earn a commission from it.</p>
          <h2>FTC Compliance</h2>
          <p>In accordance with the Federal Trade Commission (FTC) guidelines, we disclose our affiliate relationships clearly on all relevant pages. This disclosure page serves as our site-wide disclosure.</p>
